SlateportCity_SternsShipyard_1F_Text_IdrisTradeCompleted:
	.string "What is that look for? {STR_VAR_2} is\n"
	.string "harder to find than you think.$"

SlateportCity_SternsShipyard_1F_Text_IdrisTradeFailed:
